Installation of METIS subroutines.

**********************************************************************
Note: It is YOUR RESPONSIBILITY to ensure that you are entitled to
      download and use this third party package.
**********************************************************************

If you are working under Unix/Linux-like system and you have `wget'
installed, you can download the required source code for METIS
by executing the included script `get.METIS' in this directory.

Otherwise, follow those instructions:

METIS is available at

http://glaros.dtc.umn.edu/gkhome/views/metis/index.html

Please download the 'http://glaros.dtc.umn.edu/gkhome/fetch/sw/metis/metis-4.0.tar.gz'
tarball and unpack it in this directory.

tar xzf metis-4.0.tar.gz

As last step, compile METIS via 

cd metis-4.0
make

.